Updated TODOs
Refactoring - Better error handling for operators - Added test for with-ui-access
Added default error handling for commit failures - Refactoring and bug fixes
Removed done TODOs
Minor refactoring - Moved when-subscribed to utils - Better vars in observables
Refactoring and bug fix - Refactored Sampler - Added missing require
Non-code updates - better documentation - Added tools.namespace
Updated CHANGELOG for release
Bug fixes - single non container content for Panel - Allow for configuration after ctor construction
Added ToDoMVC example app
Added header click clearing, minor refactoring
Removed println tracing
Updated leiningen
Updated generated dependencies
Updated README
Refactoring - Added test for form field building - Removed dead code
Added Heirarchical container creation
Added tree, tree-table, accordian - Better hierachy construction, now includes tree-table data
Better hierachy construction - Now includes tree-table data - Added Food Menu to Sampler
Updated CHANGELOG
Added FunctionalConveter

Refactoring - more idiomatic cond statements
